node.text:
RETRO - Our new Autumn Collection ✨🍂⁠
⁠
All our new Retro designs are available as both cases & skins and the whole collection is completely customizable. ⭐ ⭐ ⭐⁠
⁠
Find your favorite design and create a custom case & skin match by adding your own images, text or trendy cliparts! ⁠
⁠
We can't wait to see you rock these nostalgic designs this season! 🤩⁠
⁠
Tag us --> @caseapp ⁠
#retrovibes #newcollection⁠
⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CASEAPP on September 01, 2021.

node.text:
⁠🍂 Autumn NEWS!! 🍂 ⁠⁠
Autumn is coming and we have some fresh designs ready for you to be perfectly in style this season! 💁⁠⁠
Discover our new ✨RETRO Collection✨ ⁠⁠
We have collected the most nostalgic retro patterns and created four brand new customizable designs for you to enjoy!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Swipe to see the patterns and colors available and leave us a comment which one is your favorite! 👇⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#newdesigns #retrovibes #caseapp⁠⁠
